sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as Saga Orchestrator
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Notify as Notification Service

    Orch->>Order: Create Order (PENDING)
    Order-->>Orch: Order Created

    Orch->>Payment: Reserve Amount
    alt 支付成功
        Payment-->>Orch: RESERVED
        Orch->>Inventory: Reserve Stock
        alt 库存充足
            Inventory-->>Orch: RESERVED
            Orch->>Payment: Confirm Payment
            Payment-->>Orch: CONFIRMED
            Orch->>Order: Update Status → CONFIRMED
            Orch-)Notify: Send Confirmation Email
        else 库存不足
            Inventory-->>Orch: FAILED
            Orch->>Payment: Cancel Reservation
            Payment-->>Orch: CANCELLED
            Orch->>Order: Update Status → FAILED
        end
    else 支付失败
        Payment-->>Orch: FAILED
        Orch->>Order: Update Status → FAILED
    end
